Maria Mauban https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maria_Mauban 0 Maria Mauban (May 10, 1924 – August 26, 2014) was a French actress. She appeared in around fifty films and television series during her career. in 1950 she starred in the British Egyptian-set crime film Cairo Road. The same year she appeared in the Ealing Studios film Cage of Gold. In 1954 she appeared in Roberto Rossellini's Journey to Italy. She was married to the industrialist Jean Versini and then to the actor Claude Dauphin. They had a child, the actor Jean-Claude Dauphin. She died on August 26, 2014.
